# TOOLS.md - Local Setup

Copy this file to `TOOLS.md` and fill in your machine-specific settings.
`TOOLS.md` is gitignored — never committed.

## Python
- Python path: `python` (or full path like `C:\Python311\python.exe`)
- Virtual environment: [path to .venv if using one]

## API Keys (optional — yfinance works without any)
- Finnhub API key: [your key from finnhub.io]
- Alpha Vantage key: [your key from alphavantage.co]

## Paths
- Reports directory: `reports/` (created automatically)
- Scripts directory: `scripts/`
- Positions file: `positions.json` (created automatically, gitignored)

## Machine-specific notes
- OS: [Windows / Linux / Mac]
- Internet: [always on / intermittent]
- Performance: This PC [is fast / has limited RAM — use --light mode]
